@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    /* Privacy Page Styles */
    .privacy-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .privacy-container h1 {
        color: #6a11cb; /* Vibrant Purple */
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-container .intro-text {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .privacy-content {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .privacy-content p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Button for demonstration */
    .privacy-container button {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #CB9E11; /* Golden Yellow */
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1em;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .privacy-container button:hover {
        background-color: #b3860f; /* Darker Yellow on Hover */
    }
</style>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="intro-text">We take your privacy seriously. Here's how we protect your data:</p>
    <div class="privacy-content">
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam scelerisque ipsum vitae lacus tincidunt, at tincidunt nunc tincidunt.</p>
        <p>Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae; Sed euismod, nisl nec aliquam aliquam, nunc nisl aliquet nunc, nec aliquam nisl nunc nec nisl.</p>
    </div>
    <button onclick="alert('Thank you for trusting us with your privacy!')">Learn More</button>
</div>